data.title: Avenue Georges Pompidou
data.meta_description:
Deskeo, 44 Avenue Georges Pompidou, 92300 Levallois, France

In the pedestrian district of Levallois, Deskeo welcomes you to its modern and fully equiped co-working center. Which is with offices ranging from 10 up to 300 m² near to the “quais de Seine”. Our serviced offices Levallois provides you fully equipped offices and meeting’s room.

We can provide you with different options, depending on your needs: a workstation, a private office or a private floor, with no commitment.

These are all included offices furnished with quality italian furniture, adjustable comfortable chairs and state-of-the-art technologies with optical fiber, Wifi (SDSL) and VoIP.

We are an all inclusive business: reception, cleaning, meeting rooms, furnished offices, high-speed internet, common areas, mail sorting. And especially a dedicated and joyful team! 

To trust Deskeo is to have access to flexible offices with no-commitment at the best rate of the market.
Book a Meeting’s room

Our offices are located near public transports and international groups headquarters such as BNP Paribas, Geodis, GMF or L’Oreal, in the heart of Levallois. Moreover, you will have access to a living district with its restaurants, coffee shops, terraces, cinemas, stores and so on.

With Deskeo, the hassle of renting is over, you can fully focus on your business.
